<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Community Guidelines - BloomBoard</title>
    <style>
        .guidelines-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: var(--content-primary);
        }
        
        .guidelines-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .guideline-card {
            background: var(--background-primary);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .guideline-card h2 {
            color: var(--content-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
        }
        
        .example-box {
            background: var(--background-secondary);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .do-dont-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        
        .do-box, .dont-box {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .do-box {
            background: #e8f5e9;
        }
        
        .dont-box {
            background: #ffebee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="guidelines-container">
        <div class="guidelines-header">
            <h1>Community Guidelines</h1>
            <p>Creating a safe and inspiring space for creativity to bloom</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
            <h2>1. Create and Share Authentically</h2>
            <p>BloomBoard is a place for authentic creative expression. We encourage original content and meaningful sharing.</p>
            
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
                <div class="do-box">
                    <h4>✓ Do This</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Share your original artwork, designs, and ideas</li>
                        <li>Credit inspiration sources and collaborators</li>
                        <li>Use appropriate tags to help others discover your content</li>
                        <li>Tell the story behind your creations</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="dont-box">
                    <h4>✗ Don't Do This</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Post content you don't have rights to use</li>
                        <li>Claim others' work as your own</li>
                        <li>Use misleading tags or descriptions</li>
                        <li>Create multiple accounts to boost engagement</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
            <h2>2. Foster Positive Interactions</h2>
            <p>Our community thrives on constructive feedback and supportive interactions.</p>
            
            <div class="example-box">
                <h4>Examples of Positive Interaction:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Offering specific, constructive feedback</li>
                    <li>Sharing techniques and tips</li>
                    <li>Celebrating others' achievements</li>
                    <li>Engaging in meaningful discussions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>We don't tolerate:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Harassment or bullying</li>
                <li>Hate speech or discrimination</li>
                <li>Trolling or inflammatory comments</li>
                <li>Spam or excessive self-promotion</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
            <h2>3. Respect Privacy and Safety</h2>
            <p>Protect yourself and others while using BloomBoard.</p>
            
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
                <div class="do-box">
                    <h4>✓ Safety Best Practices</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Use strong, unique passwords</li>
                        <li>Be mindful of sharing personal information</li>
                        <li>Report suspicious activity</li>
                        <li>Respect others' privacy settings</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="dont-box">
                    <h4>✗ Never Share</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Private contact information</li>
                        <li>Financial details</li>
                        <li>Others' personal information</li>
                        <li>Confidential business information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
            <h2>4. Content Moderation</h2>
            <p>We review reported content and take action on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Copyright violations</li>
                <li>Explicit or adult content</li>
                <li>Violence or gore</li>
                <li>Misinformation and scams</li>
                <li>Impersonation</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="example-box">
                <h4>Reporting Process:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click the "..." menu on any content</li>
                    <li>Select "Report"</li>
                    <li>Choose the violation category</li>
                    <li>Provide additional details if needed</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
            <h2>5. Consequences of Violation</h2>
            <p>Violations may result in:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Content removal</li>
                <li>Temporary account restrictions</li>
                <li>Permanent account suspension</li>
                <li>Legal action in serious cases</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>We evaluate each case considering:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Severity of violation</li>
                <li>Previous violations</li>
                <li>User's response to warnings</li>
                <li>Impact on community</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>